featureType.name: air_pollution_wzones
featureType.title: Air pollution data for the zones considered in the greater Copenhagen
featureType.abstract: This dataset contains air pollution data for the zones considered in the greater copenhagen spatial analysis report. The data consists of PM2.5, PM10, NO2, Black carbon, and the number of particles as mean values aggregated over the zones.
